1)https://github.com/wingify/rest-api-testing-framework
from this project ,can understand framework folder structure
Resolve gradle dependencies-need to configure gradle version and compactible java version in settings to run 


unable to run gradle tests
./gradlew :test --tests "PathOfClass"
gradle test --tests '*SomeTest.someSpecificFeature'
gradle test --tests '*SomeSpecificTest'
gradle test --tests "a.b.c.MyTestFile.mySingleTest"
Windows users: gradlew clean build runTests or gradlew clean build test
.\gradlew clean build test   ---->worked for me

gradle is like maven ,another build tool 




